usters-1983-21-family-friendly-Halloween-movies-TV-shows-you-can-find-on-Netflix-Amazon.html|title=21 family-friendly Halloween movies & TV shows you can find on Netflix & Amazon|date=October 22, 2015|website=Desert News|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706111836/https://www.deseretnews.com/top/3421/21/Ghostbusters-1983-21-family-friendly-Halloween-movies-TV-shows-you-can-find-on-Netflix-Amazon.html|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> Puss appears in the short film ''[[Shrek (franchise)#Donkey's Caroling Christmas-tacular|Donkey's Caroling Christmas-tacular]]'' (2010), singing his version of the song \"[[Feliz Navidad (song)|Feliz Navidad]]\".<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01pnjsx|title=Donkey's Caroling Christmas-tacular|website=[[BBC]]|access-date=September 3, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180903204856/https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01pnjsx|archive-date=September 3, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> Puss is also present in the short film ''[[Shrek (franchise)#Thriller Night|Thriller Night]]'' (2011), in which a [[zombie]] version of him is shown.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20111021005262/en/ADDING-MULTIMEDIA-Hulu-Coming-Nintendo-Systems-Nintendo|title=Adding Multimedia Hulu Plus Coming to Nintendo Systems as Nintendo 3DS Preps for 3D Video Recording|date=October 21, 2011|website=[[Business Wire]]|access-date=September 3, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180903193330/https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20111021005262/en/ADDING-MULTIMEDIA-Hulu-Coming-Nintendo-Systems-Nintendo|archive-date=September 3, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> He also appears in the short film ''[[Puss in Boots: The Three Diablos]]'' (2012), training three kittens and leading them to the right path.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-blu-ray-review/|title=Puss in Boots Blu-ray Review|date=April 1, 2012|last=Dellamorte|first=Andre|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706112216/http://collider.com/puss-in-boots-blu-ray-review/|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref name=RadioTimes/><ref name=NJ/> Puss is the protagonist of the Netflix series ''The Adventures of Puss in Boots'', protecting the city of San Lorenzo from intruders after accidentally breaking the spell that was meant to defend it;<ref name=Collider4/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.dailydot.com/upstream/puss-in-boots-netflix-future/|title=What 5 seasons of 'Puss in Boots' mean for Netflix's future|date=August 3, 2017|last=Marcus|first=Dan|website=[[The Daily Dot]]|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706124913/https://www.dailydot.com/upstream/puss-in-boots-netflix-future/|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.animationmagazine.net/top-stories/clips-whats-shaking-in-puss-in-boots-s6/|title=Clips: What's Shaking in 'Puss in Boots' S6?|date=January 26, 2018|last=Milligan|first=Mercedes|magazine=[[Animation Magazine]]|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706125949/http://www.animationmagazine.net/top-stories/clips-whats-shaking-in-puss-in-boots-s6/|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> he is also present in ''[[List of The Adventures of Puss in Boots episodes#Interactive special (2017)|Puss in Book: Trapped in an Epic Tale]]'', a television special included in the series.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-40340832|title=Netflix lets children call TV shots|date=June 20, 2017|last=Kelion|first=Leo|website=[[BBC]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828111556/https://www.bbc.com/news/technology-40340832|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://variety.com/2017/digital/news/netflix-puss-in-book-interactive-1202471301/|title=Netflix Launches 'Puss in Book,' Its First Interactive Kids Story|date=June 20, 2017|last=Roettgers|first=Janko|magazine=[[Variety (magazine)|Variety]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828105117/https://variety.com/2017/digital/news/netflix-puss-in-book-interactive-1202471301/|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2017/06/21/netflix-puss-in-boots-choose-your-own-adventure-magic/103070592/|title=What happens when Netflix lets you choose your own adventure?|date=June 21, 2017|last=Lawler|first=Kelly|newspaper=[[USA Today]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828110117/https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/tv/2017/06/21/netflix-puss-in-boots-choose-your-own-adventure-magic/103070592/|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> He will appear in the future film ''Puss in Boots 2'' as well.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/shrek-return-puss-boots-2/|title=Shrek To Return For Puss in Boots 2|date=March 27, 2015|last=De Semlyen|first=Phil|magazine=[[Empire (film magazine)|Empire]]|access-date=August 23, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823231833/https://www.empireonline.com/movies/news/shrek-return-puss-boots-2/|archive-date=August 23, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/puss-boots-2-croods-2-711450|title='Puss in Boots 2,' 'Croods 2' 'Madagascar 4' Get Release Dates|date=June 12, 2014|last=Ford|first=Rebecca|magazine=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=August 23, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823230627/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/puss-boots-2-croods-2-711450|archive-date=August 23, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/423895-antonio-banderas-says-shrek-