l]] parodying an [[Old Spice#Advertising|Old Spice advertisement]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.adweek.com/creativity/puss-boots-does-1-trillionth-isaiah-mustafaold-spice-parody-135236/|title='Puss in Boots' Does 1 Trillionth Isaiah Mustafa/Old Spice Parody|date=September 26, 2011|last=Nudd|first=Tim|website=[[Adweek]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828001222/https://www.adweek.com/creativity/puss-boots-does-1-trillionth-isaiah-mustafaold-spice-parody-135236/|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/article/2011/09/23/puss-in-boots-old-spice/|title='Puss in Boots' Old Spice trailer|date=September 23, 2011|last=Wood|first=Benjamin|magazine=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828104027/https://ew.com/article/2011/09/23/puss-in-boots-old-spice/|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gamesradar.com/puss-in-boots-gets-a-cool-old-spice-guy-tv-spot/|title=Puss in Boots gets a cool Old Spice Guy TV spot|date=September 24, 2011|last=Maytum|first=Matt|website=[[GamesRadar+]]|access-date=August 28, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180828104450/https://www.gamesradar.com/puss-in-boots-gets-a-cool-old-spice-guy-tv-spot/|archive-date=August 28, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref>\n\nPuss is a [[Player character|playable character]] in several ''Shrek'' [[Shrek (franchise)#Video games|video games]], such as ''[[Shrek 2 (video game)|Shrek 2]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/07/shrek-2-3|title=Shrek 2|date=June 7, 2004|last=Irwin|first=Mary Jane|website=[[IGN]]|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706193155/http://www.ign.com/articles/2004/06/07/shrek-2-3|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamerevolution.com/review/32387-a-gentle-giant-