e-kaboom-of-doom-synopsis/|title=First Synopses for Puss in Boots and Kung Fu Panda: The Kaboom of Doom|date=June 5, 2010|last=Bettinger|first=Brendan|website=[[Collider (website)|Collider]]|access-date=November 12, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112152416/https://collider.com/puss-in-boots-synopsis-kung-fu-panda-2-the-kaboom-of-doom-synopsis/|archive-date=November 12, 2019|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://ew.com/article/2010/06/21/puss-in-boots-spin-off/|title='Puss In Boots' spin-off details revealed. Why this could be the cat's meow.|date=June 21, 2010|last=Ward|first=Kate|magazine=[[Entertainment Weekly]]|access-date=November 12, 2019|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191112153457/https://ew.com/article/2010/06/21/puss-in-boots-spin-off/|archive-date=November 12, 2019|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> \"suave\",<ref name=Tribute/><ref name=Collider5/><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/film/hrkcf/puss-in-boots/|title=Puss in Boots|last=Jones|first=Alan|magazine=[[Radio Times]]|access-date=September 21, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180921003210/https://www.radiotimes.com/film/hrkcf/puss-in-boots/|archive-date=September 21, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all|author-link=Alan Jones (film critic)}}</ref><ref name=TheHollywoodReporter>{{cite web|url=https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/shrek-forever-after-film-review-29507|title=Shrek Forever After \u2013 Film Review|date=October 14, 2010|last=Scheck|first=Frank|magazine=[[The Hollywood Reporter]]|access-date=July 6, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180706085149/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/shrek-forever-after-film-review-29507|archive-date=July 6, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all|author-link=Frank Scheck}}</ref> \"lovable\",<ref name=RadioTimes>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiotimes.com/film/c8bzz6/puss-in-boots-the-three-diablos/|title=Puss in Boots: The Three Diablos|magazine=[[Radio Times]]|access-date=J