ick|website=[[CNET]]|access-date=September 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905115215/https://www.cnet.com/news/shrek-challenges-crash-bandicoot-for-karting-crown/|archive-date=September 5, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> He also appears in the video games ''[[Shrek video games#Educational|Shrek: Dragon's Tale]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-dragons-tale|title=Shrek: Dragon's Tale|website=[[IGN]]|access-date=September 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905121026/http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-dragons-tale|archive-date=September 5, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> ''[[Shrek video games#Educational|Shrek the Third: Arthur's School Day Adventure]]'',<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-the-third-arthurs-school-day-adventure|title=Shrek the Third: Arthur's School Day Adventure|website=[[IGN]]|access-date=September 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905121429/http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-the-third-arthurs-school-day-adventure|archive-date=September 5, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> and ''[[Shrek video games#Educational|Shrek the Third: The Search for Arthur]]''.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-the-third-the-search-for-arthur|title=Shrek the Third: The Search for Arthur|website=[[IGN]]|access-date=September 5, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180905121640/http://www.ign.com/games/shrek-the-third-the-search-for-arthur|archive-date=September 5, 2018|url-status=live|df=mdy-all}}</ref> ''[[Fruit Ninja: Puss in Boots]]'', another video game based on Puss, has also been released.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://geekdad.com/2011/10/fruit-ninja-puss-in-boots-is-a-pop-culture-mash-up/|title=Fruit Ninja: Puss in Boots Is a Pop-Culture Mash-Up|date=October 24, 2011|last=Liu|first=Jonathan H.|website=[[GeekDad]]|access-date=August 23, 2018|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180823230340/https://geekdad.com/2011/10/fruit-ninja-puss-in